Title: (CLOSED)ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥[BOUNTY]Elepig - The exchange for everyone ðŸ”¥(CLOSED)
Body: PUBLIC ANNOUNCEMENT  It is with sincere regret that we inform you that Elepig will be closing with immediate effect due to internal personal issues. It is our upmost priority to inform the Elepig community about this decision.  Our public sale will close immediately and be cancelled, all investments to date have been pledges, no ethereum has been received by the project.  We are extremely proud of all that we have accomplished this past year and could not be more thankful to those who have believed in us and invested time in Elepig.  Kind Regards  Carl Selby and Mark Williams Elepig   The above message was found in elepig LinkedIn and twitter accounts Bounty dev should address us as fast and sooner  So as to be informed the next step

Body: Multiple exchanges are already available in the cryptocurrency market. But the market is still evolving and there is room for new offerings that build on the strengths of existing tools and avoid their failings. The cryptocurrency market, and exchanges in particular, have not yet gone mainstream. This is still the age of the early adopter. Our whitepaper covers how we will make your investments simple and trusted. Alternatively, read our one pager for an overview.

Body: PROJECT SUSPENDED  Elepig Official Bounty Campaign Thread Facebook, Twitter and Linkedin rules updated w.e.f 11/06/2018    TERMS & CONDITIONS OF BOUNTY PROGRAM  1,000,000 ELEPIG tokens  will be allocated for the bounty program to be distributed to Elepig supporters after the token sale. Bounty lasts till ico ends  Week 1 Starts on Monday 28th May and all submission should be done on sunday on this thread  Each bounty task will be validated before the tokens are distributed. Only tasks that follow the bounty program terms will be eligible to receive the rewards.  Rewards Distribution BTT Signatures - 20% Translation - 15% Content Creation (Articles/Videos) - 25% Twitter - 10% Facebook -10% Telegram (Group/Individuals) -5% LinkedIn - 5% YouTube Upvotes. - 5% Bonus - 5%   GLOBAL TERMS  The bounty campaign will last until end of ICO, or until all tokens are sold out.  1) Every participant must sign up via the proper form.
